{"name":"Protect","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>An ally within 30 feet which is currently under the effect of @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.4fMSeyvD81irVye8]{Aegis Shield} takes damage from a Strike or Spell Attack.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>With the flick of your hand, you hyperconcentrate the shielding around an ally to the exact spot of an incoming blow. The target gains an amount of Resistance to all damage against the triggering attack equal to Half your Level (Rounded up) plus your Intelligence modifier. The target is then immune to Protect for 10 minutes.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["archetype","concentrate","manipulate"],"rarity":{"value":"common"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.697,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":8},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Aegis Artifact"}]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3Y8CZwu1LfMVviXx"}},"_id":"OGQfIsGTsURdBps0"}
{"name":"Sagacity Magic","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-deflect-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>This class feature replaces your Arcane School class Feature.</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>As an Artifact Sage, you rely on your Aegis as a catalyst for your magic. You add the @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.fSi741l1h9X91Ppe]{Barrier} spell to your Spellbook. You can Spontaneously spend any Prepared Spell Slot to cast Barrier at that spell slot's level, Regardless of which spell you had prepared on said spell slot. You also gain the @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.jQBttluZEUasqgKR]{Lingering Shielding} school spell.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":{"value":"common"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.697,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"classfeature"},"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vjWh4netTZPv63cA"}},"_id":"PfUOsps4SpflaXkS"}
