{"name":"Sage Spellcasting","type":"feat","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-tooled-eye-gold-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>This feature alters your Arcane Spellcasting class feature.</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Adjustments </strong>You reduce the number of spell slots you gain by 1 for each spell level you have access to (With the exception of your 10th level slot). Additionally, you can only Prepare 3 cantrips as opposed to 5. You add the @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.gRO9z8UtgITTij8f]{Aegis Blast} and @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.4fMSeyvD81irVye8]{Aegis Shield} cantrips to your spellbook. And you are always considered to have these two cantrips prepared.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":{"value":"common"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.697,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"classfeature"},"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.x69VyaEPurkiYQXP"}},"_id":"SuKqe3RivZI9CqjO"}
