{"name":"Aegis Artifact","type":"feat","img":"icons/equipment/neck/pendant-faceted-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>This class feature replaces your Arcane Thesis class feature.</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Rather than dedicate your time to creating complex theories and eloquent documents explaining the art of the Arcane. You've decided to instead put your efforts into a practical device. An @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.RM9GAKWsmjbCOHiT]{Aegis} that can channel arcane energy. An Aegis is an <strong>Uncommon </strong>item with the <strong>Arcane</strong>, <strong>Force </strong>and <strong>Magical </strong>traits. Aegis come in sets of 4 identical units which hover above the user and are commanded mentally. When not in use, they often nest on the back of the user.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Because the Aegis is unique to you, you can only own one set of Aegis at a time, and your Aegis can only be commnaded by you. Should your Aegis ever be stolen or destroyed, you can make a new set by spending 1 day of work and paying 10gp Per character level you possess.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>An Aegis can act as a weapon. By spending a single action with the Concentrate trait, the Artifact Sage can make a ranged Strike with the Aegis. This strike has a range of 30 feet; the Arcane, Force and Magical traits and deals 1d6 force damage. The Aegis is considered an simple weapon to the Artifact Sage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Any weapon runes etched onto the Aegis affect this Strike just like it would any weapon. The Aegis is considered a Ranged weapon that deals Piercing damage</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":{"value":"common"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.697,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"classfeature"},"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.O3BxMdvkWLvAANle"}},"_id":"cjv3EaizFU8BiFKT"}
