{"name":"Barrier","type":"spell","img":"modules/vyk-homebrew/assets/artifactSage/barrier.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You charge your Aegis with your own reservoir of energy and have them create a barrier of force around the target, granting them 3 Temporary Hit Points. The number of actions spent when Casting this spell determines its targets, range, area, and other parameters.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">2 </span>The spell has a range of 30 feet and grants an additional amount of Temporary Hit Points equal to your Spellcasting Ability Modifier.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">3 </span>You disperse the wave that envelops every ally within a 30-foot emanation. @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.oQByUtFczppy49Ms]{Barrier (Area)}</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1) </strong>The Temporary Hit Points granted increase by 3.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["force"],"rarity":{"value":"uncommon"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.697,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"heal"},"category":{"value":"spell"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"abjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":"An Equipped Aegis"},"target":{"value":"1 Willing or Unconscious creature"},"range":{"value":"varies"},"area":{"value":"","areaType":""},"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":"1 Minute"},"damage":{"value":{"1gwv0c5r8kq0uvju":{"value":"3","type":{"value":"temphp","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":true}}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"autoHeightenLevel":{"value":null},"scaling":{"interval":1,"damage":{"1gwv0c5r8kq0uvju":"3"}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"enhanced-terrain-layer":{"multiple":1,"min":0