{"name":"Lingering Shielding","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/time/arrows-circling-pink.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You channel power to your Aegis and send it into Overdrive to enhance your shielding. Make an Arcana check. The DC is usually a standard-difficulty DC of a level equal to your level. The effect depends on the result of your check.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your next Aegis Shield action lasts for 4 rounds.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your next Aegis Shield action lasts for 3 rounds.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>Your next Aegis Shield action lasts for 1 round, but you don't spend the Focus Point for casting this spell.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>@Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage-macros.oYoWBpcUKTPzM9OU]{Lingering Shielding}</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":{"value":"uncommon"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.697,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":"An Equipped Aegis"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":"","areaType":""},"time":{"value":"free"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"autoHeightenLevel":{"value":null}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"enhanced-terrain-layer":{"multiple":1,"min":0,"max":0,"environment":""},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6Mqdz4zZA4puXzdz"}},"_id":"jQBttluZEUasqgKR"}
