{"_id":"RgoGZaT58ZTYfTJn","name":"Artifact Sage (Class Archetype)","type":"feat","img":"icons/equipment/shield/heater-crystal-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>Clever engineers of both magic and machine. These sages put their life's work into creating specialized devices called Aegis to produce all manner of powerful protective and offensive magical effects.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>While uncommon in nature, Artifact Sages can be found all over Golarion. From the prestigious schools of Magaambya to smaller studies of the arcane in the far corners of Tian Xia- Artifact Sages have sprung to create suspiciously similar devices called an Aegis. An arcane construction capable of handling energy in the form of Force. From blasting down foes to creating barriers. Artifact Sages often take reign of combat through these Aegis devices.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>No one knows why these sages end up arriving at the same overall design or purpose of these Aegis artifacts. Some say it is the work of divine inspiration. Others say it is an elaborate conspiracy involving mad goblins and time travel. But more sensible folk arrive at the conclusion that the Aegis' design is simply the most efficient use of the resources being allocated. Regardless. When you spot an Artifact Sage, expect to see powerful magic at work.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Artifact Sage (Class Archetype)</h1>\n<p>Through your own tinkering and hard work, you've managed to create your own version of an Aegis. An arcane device capable of channeling Force-aspected energy in a variety of ways.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><strong>If you take this Archetype, you must take the @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.ZQxhY6tB9I0rCDFg]{Artifact Sage Dedication} feat as your 2nd level Class feat.</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites </strong>You must be a Wizard.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>@Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.cjv3EaizFU8BiFKT]{Aegis Artifact} (1st)</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>@Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.SuKqe3RivZI9CqjO]{Sage Spellcasting} (1st)</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>@Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.PfUOsps4SpflaXkS]{Sagacity Magic} (1st)</h2>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":{"value":"uncommon"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.709,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-01-01T12:12:04.411-04:00","version":{"schema":0.697,"foundry":"9.238","system":"3.1.3.9639"}}},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"classfeature"},"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.UHJE668g0S93v1bx"}}}
{"_id":"Rz1H4pVwX4BrcHrS","name":"Hyperbeam","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-red-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You combine the strength of all of your Aegi and fire a devastating beam. All creatures caught in the line take 12d4 Force damage (basic Reflex save against your Spell DC).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Special </strong>If this action is performed while under the Effects of @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.JSEvPDDNLa4z4aP2]{Hypercharge}, increase the damage dice of Hyperbeam to d6s.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.bvYlzKj3Xwgo4rma]{Hyperbeam (Hypercharged)}</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightening (+1) </strong>The damage increases by 2d4</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["force"],"rarity":{"value":"common"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.709,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-01-01T12:12:04.482-04:00","version":{"schema":0.697,"foundry":"9.238","system":"3.1.3.9639"}}},"level":{"value":8},"spellType":{"value":"save"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":"An Equipped Aegis"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":"100","areaType":"line"},"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{"te3vclz8l5fcmae1":{"value":"12d4","type":{"value":"force","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"save":{"value":"reflex","basic":"basic"},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"autoHeightenLevel":{"value":null},"scaling":{"interval":1,"damage":{"te3vclz8l5fcmae1":"2d4"}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"enhanced-terrain-layer":{"multiple":1,"min":0,"max":0,"environment":""},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vJhxcvxzzTWPaIVF"}}}
{"_id":"SuKqe3RivZI9CqjO","name":"Sage Spellcasting","type":"feat","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-tooled-eye-gold-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>This feature alters your Arcane Spellcasting class feature.</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Adjustments </strong>You reduce the number of spell slots you gain by 1 for each spell level you have access to (With the exception of your 10th level slot). Additionally, you can only Prepare 3 cantrips as opposed to 5. You add the @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.gRO9z8UtgITTij8f]{Aegis Blast} and @Compendium[vyk-homebrew.artifact-sage.4fMSeyvD81irVye8]{Aegis Shield} cantrips to your spellbook. And you are always considered to have these two cantrips prepared.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":{"value":"common"},"custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.709,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-01-01T12:12:04.419-04:00","version":{"schema":0.697,"foundry":"9.238","system":"3.1.3.9639"}}},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"classfeature"},"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"MIb5Ldg8TLeVngZ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.x69VyaEPurkiYQXP"}}}
